Package com.esri.mo2.map.ext

Supports geocoding and stored query operations.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ExtractExtension Implements an Extract LayerExtension, that is used for layers involved in data downloading activities from an ArcIMS ExtractService.
GeoCodeExtension Defines a LayerExtension that can be used for geocoding.
GeoCodeStyle Defines an address-matching style.
StoredQuery Defines a parameterized QueryFilter.
StoredQueryExtension Contains one or more StoredQuery objects.
 

Class Summary
BaseExtractExtension Implements a base Extract LayerExtension, that is used for layers involved in data downloading activities from an ArcIMS ExtractService.
BaseGeoCodeExtension This implementation of GeoCodeExtension can be used to define a GeoCode LayerExtension for a particular FeatureLayer.
BaseGeoCodeStyle A standard implementation of GeoCodeStyle that is defined by java.util.Properties.
BaseStoredQuery Standard implementation of StoredQuery.
BaseStoredQueryExtension A standard implementation of StoredQueryExtension that holds one or more StoredQuery objects.
OutputField This object provides proper ArcXML serialization/desesialization of an Extract layer extension.
Registry A LayerExtension registry can be used by another Component that is responsible for deserializing LayerExtensions from AXL.
 

Package com.esri.mo2.map.ext Description

Supports geocoding and stored query operations.
